{"word":"G327 - ἀναζητέω - anazētéō - an-ad-zay-teh'-o - Seek","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναζητέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anazētéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ad-zay-teh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Seek</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தேடு"},{"paragraph":"to seek out, search through, make diligent search"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G2212 - ζητέω - zētéō - dzay-teh'-o/2212\">G2212</a>; to <i>search</i> out: - seek.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}